Package schedule

Class Summary
Affinity Affinity contains the affinity information for each department.
Building Building contains the data for various buildings on campus.
Classroom Classroom contains the data for each bookable classroom, as well as the means to reserve each room.
Course Course contains the various data for individual courses.
Course.CoreCodes CoreCodes are supplemental data corresponding to SAS requirements fulfilled by the course.
CourseCondensed CourseCondensed is a distilled version of a Course, Section, and MeetingTime.
Instructor Instructor contains information regarding course instructors.
Location Location contains location information for each Building.
Major Major contains course information pertaining to different majors.
MeetingTime MeetingTime contains information about Course meeting times.
Schedule Schedule is the main driver of the scheduling process.
Section Section contains information about Course sections.
Section.Comments Comments contains supplemental information pertaining to each section.
